-
    var currPage = $i18n.PAGES[4];
    htmlAttrs = currPage.htmlAttrs;


include /pug/includes/head
body(class=$i18n.lang)
    include /pug/includes/header
    app-about
        .screen-main
            .container
                h1 Our mission is to simplify blockchain adoption by enterprises and governments
        .screen-experience
            .container
                section
                    article
                        h1 7
                        p years of blockchain development
                    article
                        h1 45
                        p people are contributing to our mission
                    article
                        h1 20
                        p successful proof-of-concepts
        #mission_container.screen-mission
            .overlay
            #mission_object.container
                article
                    h2 Our mission
                    p
                        | &#x9;&#x9;&#x9;&#x9;Smart implementation of blockchain redefines the trust we place in each other, making interactions more transparent, fair and reliable. This is why we will impact on the World Happiness Index, giving everyone access to knowledge, integrating developing countries into the global economy and
                        strong &nbsp; bringing joy to people&rsquo;s lives
                        | .
                img.img-1.lazy(data-src='/assets/images/about/mission-1.png' alt='')
                img.img-2.lazy(data-src='/assets/images/about/mission-2.png' alt='')
                img.img-3(src='/assets/images/about/mission-3.png' alt='')
                img.img-4(src='/assets/images/about/mission-4.png' alt='')

        .screen-history(style="display:none")
            .container
                h2
                    | Here is our history
                    small Drag it
                .swiper-container.history-story
                    .swiper-wrapper
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 2011
                            p
                                | Oleg Strelenko, the founder of the project, started creating his own cryptocurrency: DCoin.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 April 2014
                            p
                                | Release of DCoin: a cryptocurrency viable without exchanges, banks and other mediators. 66 types of transactions, 77 currencies, video identification and an integrated exchange system for converting DCoin into cash.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 December 2014
                            p
                                | DCoin rewritten from PHP to Go (more than 73,000 lines of code). Works on Win (64/32), OSX (64/32), Linux (64/32), FreeBSD (64/32), Android, IOS, supports PostgreSQL, SQLite, MySQL.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 January 2016
                            p DCoin attracts its first investor.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 June 2016
                            p
                                | Work starts on creating the first blockchain platform prototype as part of the Daylight project. The first office opens in Moscow.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 October 2016
                            p
                                | The first versions of the web system, plus Simvolio and Prototypo programming languages are created. The project is renamed as eGaaS (electronic Government as a Service).
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 Spring 2017
                            p
                                | The test network is launched. The concept and ideology of smart contracts alongside a platform legal system is developed. The proof of concept for the first projects is validated for the UAE, India and Luxembourg.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 July 2017
                            p An office is opened in Luxembourg.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 August 2017
                            p
                                | The platform&rsquo;s application is expanded so that it may be implemented outside of eGovernment. Apla is born: a team of experts for developing and integrating blockchain solutions. eGaaS is accepted into the Luxembourg centre for fintech.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 Autumn 2017
                            p
                                | Proprietary products (programming client, Simvolo and Protypo languages) are perfected. The visual editor and builder for interfaces is created.
                        article.swiper-slide
                            h4 By 2018
                            p
                                | Apla Enterprise Network (AEN) blockchain network is launched for business. The network speed is increased by 5-10 times (to 1,500 tx/s). Offices open in Dubai, Singapore and New York.
        .screen-team
            .container
                h2 Leadership
                p
                    | Leadership in innovations makes an impact on a global scale. Multicultural, multidisciplinary and diverse top-management allows Apla to speak in one language with worldwide leaders from prime ministers to CIOs.
                    br
                    br
                    | Our leaders eat last. Creating a workplace of the future: bureaucracy free, with a greater purpose, based on constant learning and individuality at its core.
                +team-list('TOPMANAGMENT')
                h2 Team is everything
                p
                    | Welcome to the world where everyone&rsquo;s invited to form deep, meaningful connections.
                +team-list('TEAM')
        .screen-vacancies
            .container
                h2 Take part in our journey
                p
                    | Are you a technical specialist, sales manager, designer, maker, dreamer, Sarah, Alan - a purpose driven individual? Make a real impact: build the future you want to live in - &nbsp;
                    a(href='mailto:hr@apla.io') send us a CV!
                //h4 Vacant positions
                //+vacancy-list()
                //h3
                    | Even if you have not found a&nbsp;suitable position  &mdash;
                    a(href='mailto:hr@apla.io') send us a CV!
                p We are always in search for great talent.
        .screen-media_info
            .container
                h2 Media informaion
                section
                    article
                        h5 Apla logotype and guideline
                        // <p>Unlock the creativity of software developers to deliver new apps and services to customers faster. Gain the freedom to build the right app with the right components and accelerate digital strategies.</p>
                    div
                        h5
                            a(href='/assets/media_assets.zip') Download Logotypes &amp; Guidelines
                        p Archive .ZIP, 3.3 MB
                        small
                            | Guidelines &mdash; .PDF, 1.9 MB
                            br
                            | Logotypes &mdash; .AI, 1.6 MB
                section
                    article
